33,"uid":79077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T00:30:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f0d6162a09b4236d00bdd1f251d073467a3f746e","tid":554433,"uid":64696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d8fdadef4771557478e16afb2ddecf4390a937e7","tid":554433,"uid":31355,"like":160,"dislike":13,"score":147,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T14:19:35.000Z","msg":"通常呢d四眼仔 拖住條女 <br />\n就以為自己高人一等<br />\n成日係度瞄嘴瞄舌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T00:33:13.000Z","msg":"毒撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b97437ec98fe225c2b1830895df0cbdbc5c279d1","tid":554433,"uid":92467,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T00:34:24.000Z","msg":"《<del> 毒男 </del><span style=\"color: red;\">樓主</span>的ㄧ生》<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n升中四了，還未試過拍拖，但毒男說：「不緊要，依家努力讀書考好會考，第時有錢你慌無女？」<br />\n<br />\n結果，毒男克服了一個又一個的考試，升上大學；影畢業相時，發覺好多人都一雙一對，原來大學係撮合情侶既好地方。毒男依然一個，但他說：「不緊要，即將係我踏入社會大展拳腳既時候，亦係我幸福生活既開始！」<br />\n<br />\n毒男努力工作，三年，五年，七年過去了，依然單身。但他終於達成了心願，成為高收入人仕 － 月薪達二萬零五百蚊。<br />\n<br />\n毒男年過三十，開始疑惑：「點解我已經係成功人仕，但仲係無女？」更令他驚訝的是，公司不少女同事都同MK型男拍拖結婚，但那些男人可不是事業型喎，例如，Dorothy既男朋友只係中五畢業既Sales，月薪只有一萬八千蚊，比自己足足少了二千多元！點解？唔係努力讀書成為有錢人就有女既咩？<br />\n<br />\n不知不覺毒男到了中年，身邊已無什麼朋友，自己渡過一個又一個既聖誕節及情人節。<br />\n<br />\n毒男年老了，孤零零一個坐在公園，回想一生：「自己曾得過什麼？女人的身體是怎麼樣的？和女朋友係海邊共渡平安夜既滋味係點架？高登人不是經常留帖話：『後生時唔好浪費時間，第時有錢你荒無女咩！』我照做了，究竟什麼地方出錯？"},{"pid":"82f794a705c284ea7297fe2aff67943787556785","tid":554433,"uid":170004,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T00:50:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/09/085033_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F09%2F085033_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=af6e7a65&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b0b45c075f34a7106e8620434c4b4a8da22bbb09","tid":554433,"uid":86607,"like":1,"dislike":15,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T00:57:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5a3706f8d607119067cba3024d8722efecc33e10","tid":554433,"uid":36049,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T01:01:04.000Z","msg":"成個弱智咁都拖女<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f944d80653bcad6689fedc84a0332fb87c5aa15e","tid":554433,"uid":12772,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a4ba054de3f74c5176dec99779c8d49f8fdcd6ae","tid":554433,"uid":34771,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"fd6e2508f6f29adc1bb5960d1e94f7a7395a21bb","tid":554433,"uid":12772,"like":47,"dislike":5,"score":42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T17:19:42.000Z","msg":"因為人地有腦 但你無囉柒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你無女就檢討自己 人地點樣關你條毒撚撚事咩 <br />\n況且有幾可係街見到兩個都正既組合？  <br />\nbetween 條女咁都話正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你驗完腦應該要驗埋眼"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T17:20:39.000Z","msg":"況且有幾可係街見到兩個都正既組合？ <br />\n因為正嘅人唔多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T01:01:15.000Z","msg":"女都仲話可以化妝幫下 男既就<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34b1097d06838a77ab738d782b872dbf6f0fffac","tid":554433,"uid":4917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T01:02:06.000Z","msg":"正條撚"},{"pid":"514dd86a2a54c96fafce105f7bbc199f31c29c7c","tid":554433,"uid":85629,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"34b1097d06838a77ab738d782b872dbf6f0fffac","tid":554433,"uid":4917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-0